            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20200619_Smith_Tommy_Q2</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>Can you tell us about what drove you to begin working with Samaritan's Purse? Can you tell us about Samaritan's Purse?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 2</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:04:36"
                            endTime="00:06:06">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20200619_Smith_Tommy_Q3</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>What was the experience of receiving the call to go to Gatlinburg like?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 3</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:06:06"
                            endTime="00:06:57">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20200619_Smith_Tommy_Q4</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>So you were already following what was happening on the news before receiving a call?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 4</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:06:57"
                            endTime="00:08:36">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20200619_Smith_Tommy_Q5</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>After getting to Gatlinburg, what transpired? What does the Samaritan's Purse operation look like? How does it take shape?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 5</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:08:36"
                            endTime="00:09:35">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20200619_Smith_Tommy_Q6</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>You were stationed at the First Baptist Church in Gatlinburg? What was it like when you arrived a week after the fire?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 6</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:09:35"
                            endTime="00:12:01">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20200619_Smith_Tommy_Q7</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>Can you tell us about the experiences you had at the sites of homeowners where you were sifting through ashes?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 7</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:12:01"
                            endTime="00:13:14">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20200619_Smith_Tommy_Q8</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>Was this the first wildfire that you assisted on with Samaritan's Purse?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 8</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:13:14"
                            endTime="00:35:42">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20200619_Smith_Tommy_Q9</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>Are there any other specific memories from meeting with these homeowners?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 9</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:35:42"
                            endTime="00:39:06">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20200619_Smith_Tommy_Q10</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>What kind of impact did this deployment have on you emotionally or spiritually?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 10</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:39:06"
                            endTime="00:44:49">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20200619_Smith_Tommy_Q11</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>Have you gone back to Gatlinburg since the deployment?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 11</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:44:49"
                            endTime="00:41:58">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20200619_Smith_Tommy_Q12</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>After going back, does it seem like the community is recovering from the event?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
